A developer wrote the following IAM policy and attached it to an IAM user. The user reports they **cannot** upload files to the `reports/` prefix in the bucket.

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-bucket/reports/*"
    },
    {
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-bucket/reports/*"
    }
  ]
}
```

What is the root cause?
